'''布萊特·拜爾'''（{{lang-en|William Bret Baier}}，{{bd|1970年|8月4日}}）是美國的一位新聞主播，現在在福斯新聞台主持Special Report with Bret Baier節目，並且是福斯新聞台的資深政治主播<ref name="washingtonpost">{{cite news|title=Bret Baier, the Successor to Brit Hume on Fox's 'Special Report'|newspaper=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|publisher=[[The_Washington_Post_Company|The Washington Post Company]]|date=January 6, 2009|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/01/05/AR2009010503271.html|accessdate=September 29, 2010|archive-date=2017-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170609212424/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/01/05/AR2009010503271.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在此之前他曾是無線電視網的白宮和五角大樓記者。他已經結婚並育有二子<ref>{{cite news|last=Roberts|first=Roxanne|authorlink=Roxanne Roberts|author2=Argetsinger, Amy|authorlink2=Amy Argetsinger|title=''The Reliable Source'': Love, etc.: Bret Baier, Rachel Dratch, Ed Swiderski and Jillian Harris|newspaper=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|publisher=[[The_Washington_Post_Company|The Washington Post Company]]|date=July 8, 2010|url=http://voices.washingtonpost.com/reliable-source/2010/07/love_etc_snl_star_rachel_dratc.html|accessdate=June 12, 2011|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304223547/http://voices.washingtonpost.com/reliable-source/2010/07/love_etc_snl_star_rachel_dratc.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
